sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant Auth as AuthPage / AuthForm
    participant S as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as Postgres (profiles, user_roles, organization_members)
    participant App as AuthProvider (src/hooks/useAuth.tsx)
    participant Q as TanStack Query
    participant T as Telemetry (PostHog)

    U->>Auth: Submit credentials
    Auth->>S: supabase.auth.signInWithPassword (or OAuth)
    S-->>Auth: { session, user }
    S->>App: onAuthStateChange(SIGNED_IN)
    App->>App: setSession
    App->>App: setUser (buildSessionDerivedUser - sync)
    par Async profile enrichment
        App->>DB: SELECT profiles WHERE user_id = ...
        App->>DB: SELECT user_roles WHERE user_id = ...
        App->>DB: SELECT organization_members WHERE user_id = ... AND status='active'
        App->>DB: load notification preferences
    end
    DB-->>App: profile + roles + org + notifPrefs
    App->>App: setUser (transformUser - enriched)
    App->>Q: prefetchQuery user-trips
    App->>T: identify { id, display_name, is_pro, organization_id }
    App-->>U: render protected routes
